<event name="PROTON_HAUNT_DEFEAT">
	<text>目标被击毙后，你忍不住瞄了一眼他们带了什么货。里面有一些看上去像远古武器的东西。</text>
	<weapon name="GIFTLIST_ANCIENT_BASIC" />
	<unlockCustomShip silent="false">PLAYER_SHIP_GHOST_2</unlockCustomShip>
</event>

